01:30:04,610 --> 01:30:05,694
Rebornsy?
<font color="#ffff54">Tái sinh?</font>

1295
01:30:05,777 --> 01:30:07,821
- Reblanksy.
- Blanksy.
<font color="#ffff54">- Reblanksy.
- Mệt mỏi.</font>

